  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "5DjPVBSDcyhygKj/9f0E7lJxfKc=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:44.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# style editors with tailwind classes or scoped style tags\n\nTwo styling approaches for editors:\n\n1. **Tailwind classes** \u2014 Preferred. Apply utility classes directly to elements.\n2. **Scoped style tags** \u2014 When Tailwind is insufficient. Make selectors specific to the editor component to prevent global CSS leakage.\n\n```tsx\n// \u2705 Tailwind\n<div className=\"flex gap-4 p-6 rounded-lg border\">\n\n// \u2705 Scoped style tag\n<style>{`\n  .my-editor-name .custom-table { border-collapse: collapse; }\n  .my-editor-name .custom-table td { padding: 8px; }\n`}</style>\n\n// \u274c Unscoped \u2014 will affect the entire app\n<style>{`\n  table { border-collapse: collapse; }\n  td { padding: 8px; }\n`}</style>\n```\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[editor patterns]]",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:44.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:44.000Z"
    }
  },
